abstract: Capt Rene Zeetsen and First Lt Ernst Mollinger, United Nations peacekeepers from the Netherlands, die when Apache helicopter they were riding in during military exercise crashes near Gao in northern Mali.
lead_paragraph: Two Dutch peacekeepers died Tuesday in a helicopter crash during a military exercise in northern Mali, Dutch and United Nations officials said.

headline.print_headline: Africa; Mali: 2 Peacekeepers Die in Crash
